title: AWS Lightsail
pid: 44da28be-3419-46e8-a07b-e46111a183f2
body: |2-
  A higher-level interface to [[id:da25bd69-a967-4393-bfa7-817f4c7eaa47][AWS EC2]].
  Hides many configuration details, e.g. security.
  Has been accused of burying errors in logs and being harder to manipulate outside of its default parameters.
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
